msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1941_11-ger_moscow/outro_failed_hq"
msgid ""
"The soviets managed to launch a successful counterattack that pushed the "
"Wehrmacht further back than the starting positions of Operation Typhoon. In "
"spite of all efforts, the Germans were unable to enter the Soviet capital. "
"After learning the harsh lessons of the Soviet winter, German high command "
"shifted focus to the next summer offensive."
msgstr ""
"Los soviéticos consiguieron lanzar un exitoso contraataque que hizo "
"retroceder a la Wehrmacht más allá de las posiciones de partida de la "
"Operación Tifón. A pesar de todos los esfuerzos, los alemanes fueron "
"incapaces de entrar en la capital soviética. Tras aprender las duras "
"lecciones del invierno soviético, el alto mando alemán se centró en la "
"siguiente ofensiva de verano."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1941_11-ger_moscow/story"
msgid "OPERATION TYPHOON - Krasnaya Polyana\n\nBriefing: The ultimate goal of Army Group Centre is at stake. The Soviet capital, right in our sights! We underestimated the enemy's strength. The only way to reach a decisive victory will be a full-blown frontal assault. Today we risk everything! To arms, Kameraden!\n\nGoals:\n - Advance into Moscow.\n - Demoralization of the Soviet people.\n - Destruction of the Red Army's capability for command and control."
msgstr ""
"OPERACIÓN TIFÓN - Krasnaya Polyana,\n"
"Informe:#El objetivo final del Grupo de Ejércitos Centro está en juego - \n"
"\n"
"\n"
" \n"
"¡La capital soviética, justo en nuestra mira!\n"
"\n"
"Hemos subestimado la fuerza del enemigo.\n"
"\n"
"La única manera de alcanzar una victoria decisiva será\n"
"\n"
"será un ataque frontal completo.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"¡Hoy lo arriesgamos todo! ¡A las armas, Kameraden!.\n"
"\n"
" \n"
"Objetivos:\n"
"\n"
"- Avanzar hacia Moscú.\n"
"\n"
"- Destrucción de la capacidad del Ejército Rojo \n"
"\n"
"de mando y control.\n"
"\n"
"- Desmoralización del pueblo soviético"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1941_11-ger_moscow/narrator_start0"
msgid ""
"Welcome to the front line, Major! This is our field HQ, it must remain in "
"our control!"
msgstr ""
"¡Bienvenido al frente, Mayor! Este es nuestro cuartel general de campo, "
"¡debe permanecer bajo nuestro control!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1941_11-ger_moscow/narrator_start1"
msgid ""
"Attention Soldaten! The Bolsheviks have tightened the grip with which they "
"hold their precious capital city. Today we will demonstrate that the mighty "
"Wehrmacht cannot be stopped. They may have the numbers, but nothing "
"outclasses our combat effectiveness and combat experience. Soldiers of the "
"Reich - forward, to victory!"
msgstr ""
"¡Atención Soldaten! Los bolcheviques han apretado el agarre con el que "
"mantienen su preciosa capital. Hoy demostraremos que la poderosa Wehrmacht "
"no puede ser detenida. Puede que tengan los números, pero nada supera "
"nuestra eficacia y experiencia de combate. Soldados del Reich - ¡adelante, a "
"la victoria!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1941_11-ger_moscow/narrator_start2"
msgid ""
"The Red Army is bringing in reserves from Siberia and will mount massive "
"counterattacks. Be ready for anything!"
msgstr ""
"El Ejército Rojo está trayendo reservas de Siberia y montará contraataques "
"masivos. ¡Prepárate para todo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1941_11-ger_moscow/narrator_start3"
msgid ""
"Begin securing the objectives, meanwhile more reinforcements are being "
"prepared for deployment!"
msgstr ""
"Comienza a asegurar los objetivos, ¡mientras se preparan más refuerzos para "
"ser despliegados!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1941_11-ger_moscow/allied_enemy_near_hq"
msgid "Soldaten! Soviets are close to our Field HQ!"
msgstr "¡Soldaten! ¡Los soviéticos están cerca de nuestro cuartel general!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1941_11-ger_moscow/player_enemy_near_hq"
msgid "We must hold the command post! We cannot afford to abandon it!"
msgstr ""
"¡Debemos mantener el puesto de mando! ¡No podemos permitirnos abandonarlo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1941_11-ger_moscow/hq_bonus"
msgid "Major! Now you can request an airstrikes."
msgstr "¡Mayor! Ahora puede solicitar un ataque aéreo."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1941_11-ger_moscow/allied_enemypara"
msgid "Watch the skies, Soviet paratroopers!"
msgstr "¡Cuidado con los cielos, paracaidistas soviéticos!"
